rows.label: qst700903_msg0001
rows.name: The trail ends here.

rows.label: qst700903_msg0002
rows.name:
Our mystery opponent must have
scaled the cliff. Or perhaps soared
up and over...

rows.label: qst700903_msg0003
rows.name:
Are we talking about the same beast,
Prince? Our stompy, tramply friend?
Now it has wings, is that it?

rows.label: qst700903_msg0004
rows.name:
That would be a curious and
fascinating development, no?

rows.label: qst700903_msg0005
rows.name:
Um...
It cannot have simply vanished, can it?

rows.label: qst700903_msg0006
rows.name:
Don't be stupid. It's a dumb animal,
running around in circles.

rows.label: qst700903_msg0007
rows.name:
Oh, yes, of course. How silly of me.
It's not like ghosts actually exist...

rows.label: qst700903_msg0008
rows.name: Oh my. Kasumi, are you afraid of ghosts?

rows.label: qst700903_msg0009
rows.name:
N-n-nonsense! I'm just...
concerned about the possibility...

rows.label: qst700903_msg0010
rows.name:
...I see. Very well then.
I should probably not mention THAT.

rows.label: qst700903_msg0011
rows.name:
Huh?
Wh-what do you mean, "THAT"?

rows.label: qst700903_msg0012
rows.name: Oh, don't you feel its presence?

rows.label: qst700903_msg0013
rows.name: Even though it's...right behind you?

rows.label: qst700903_msg0014
rows.name: Eeeeeeek!

rows.label: qst700903_msg0015
rows.name: Kagutsuchi stop.

rows.label: qst700903_msg0016
rows.name: Don't you think that was mean, Kagutsuchi?

rows.label: qst700903_msg0017
rows.name:
Oh, I'm sorry. I didn't actually think
she would fall for it...

rows.label: qst700903_msg0018
rows.name:
Laura-sama, please..
There are no ghosts, right? Ghosts
don't exist...do they?

rows.label: qst700903_msg0019
rows.name:
You'll have to excuse Kasumi.
This is her one weakness.

rows.label: qst700903_msg0020
rows.name:
It's all right, Kasumi. If we ever see a
ghost, which we won't, I promise I'll
chase it away for you. Good?

rows.label: qst700903_msg0021
rows.name:
Now, now, Kagutsuchi. You needn't
pout like a chided schoolchild.

rows.label: qst700903_msg0022
rows.name:
You've shown us a side of you we don't
often get to see. That alone is worth
noting.

rows.label: qst700903_msg0023
rows.name: Th-thank you, Majesty.

rows.label: qst700903_msg0024
rows.name:
...Come on, all of you.
All this fawning is making me itchy.

rows.label: qst700903_msg0025
rows.name: Fine, fine.

rows.label: qst700903_msg0026
rows.name:
It seems the trail has gone cold.
Let's go back and report on our
investigation so far.
